item.title: Project 1
item.description: INTRODUCTION The two datasets chosen are MathAchieve and MathAchSchool. Both relate Achievement Scores in Mathematics to different variables which have been the focus of study for many articles in the modern world. MathAchieve contains the School number, status of being a Minority, Sex of the individual, Socioeconomic Status (SES), a numeric vector of mathematics achievement score (MathAch), and a numeric vector of the mean SES for the entire school.
